{"type": "article", "id": 24531, "title": "蛇形台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-28T06:04:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152522G3bPTaDrVgytL78W.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏弯曲的台灯在形态上像一条蛇，也令人想起维纳·潘顿的“S”型椅，一张试图用一块板材制造出一把有完整外壳的椅子。台灯的底座使用氯丁橡胶（Neoprene）材料，底座是一个轻微的转折并与桌面形成了三角空间，很稳定。台灯的支柱是逐渐变细的，流畅的曲线让这盏灯保持了轻盈。而最上面连接了一个圆形的小灯，灯光柔和。这盏灯产自意大利，有 7 种颜色选择，售价 199 欧元起，<a href=\"http://www.limelab.it/shop-eur/\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152521s6p2voLg7HVCZUkN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.68380952\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152521arHGSXU0J5pNlD16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152521k24a83s60VtxAmPl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152522wLQFcPsokN0tiVKE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}